metadata.name: Welcome to Zombie Land
metadata.description:
Yoo what? Shitt zombies ruunn
Let me get my Melons... Welcome to Zombie Land

Collectors will receive a high-res GIF Format and also a 4k video format file, wallpaper, and a banner. IM ALSO PLANNING TO GIVE A PHYSICAL NFT PIECE IN THE FUTURE...
